					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>States that the village of <hi rend="bold">Iḍupulapāḍu</hi> in the <hi rend="bold">Karmarāshṭra</hi> was originally granted by <hi rend="bold">Mukkaṇṭi Pallava</hi> to certain Brahmins of <hi rend="italic">Kāṇva-Śākhā</hi> and that king <hi rend="bold">Gaṇapatidēva</hi> regranted it to the Brahmins. Contains a list of the donees and their shares.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
